  "title": "Product Engineer",
  "description": "<ul><li>Knowledge in creating & modifying BOM structure.</li><li>Knowledge of SFC (Shop floor control) system & SAP maintenance.</li><li>Understanding of rack packaging design.</li><li>Lead and drive to execute BOM/ Materials changes and drive toward smooth  transition & implementation with cross-functional teams from internal & Overseas</li><li>To support production on mass run.</li><li>To lead/participate in Kaizen activities.</li><li>Support in factory NPI qualification.</li><li>Participate in ISO audit both internally and externally<strong>.</strong></li></ul><p><strong>Requirements: </strong></p><ul><li>Degree/ Diploma in Engineering with at least 3 years of <strong>relevant working experience in server, rack build, semiconductor manufacturing background</strong></li><li>Hand-on experience in <strong>SAP,BOM and Agile </strong></li><li>Ability to work with the customer, HQ / factory, Peers / Subordinate, and Superior</li><li>Strong problem-solving skills.</li></ul><p>WE REGRET TO INFORM THAT ONLY SHORTLISTED CANDIDATES WILL BE NOTIFIED</p><p>Manfield Employment Services Pte Ltd<br />EA Licence No:    95C2823<br />Posting Personnel:   Quennie Chen<br />EA Personnel Registration No:  R1222837</p>",
